detailedRequirements:
Task Overview

The goal of this challenge is to display awards widget of logged in user and fix styling of existing awards widget.

Task Requirements

  • Fix "Awards" widget (see screenshot) styling
    • Remove award-item class so that the background image does not get displayed along with the award image we pull from backend.
    • The award row should have same styling as in Playgame-loggedin.html in provided prototype
      • Should be displaying user image instead of username
      • There is a border and padding .. etc of other styling applying to the award image.
      • Award image actual height width should be reduced to fit the 41x38 image wrapper
      • When hovering over the award image it should show the image with it's actual size.
      • When hovering over the award image it should show tooltip with name of the award.
      • Keep the table column headers as in the code. It is missing in prototype.
  • Implement "My Awards" widget as shown in screenshot, it is appened below user widget info
    • It should match Playgame-loggedin.html
    • When hovering over the award image it should show image in it's original size as popup
    • When hovering over the award image it should show a tooltip with the name of the award
    • You are only implementing "latest awards", don't implement "Latest Badges"
    • Rename "Latest Awards" title to "My Awards"
    • The logic to retrieve this information is same as "Awards" widget except that we are passing the username to search for it's awards
    • If user has NO awards then hide the div. Don't even display "My Awards" title.
    • This code should only execute if a user is logged in.

Github Private Repo

Files exists in private github repository. If you don't have access to links below, please post in challenge forums to request access.

Source code exists in csfv_minisite_frontend_module (branch minisite4)

UI Prototype exists in csfv_ui_prototypes (use Ghostmap folder)

Deliverables

  • Patch file of changes.
  • Text file with any notes to reviewer.
